column18:
Welcome



Thank you for your interest in participating in this study. This study is run by a team of researchers at HEC Lausanne and LMU Munich. Before you begin, it is important that you are informed about the procedure of this research. Please read the following information carefully. 



Any research data published in scientific journals or elsewhere will be anonymous and cannot be traced back to you. This anonymized data will be made publicly available. About this study

	Participation will take around 10 minutes.
	You participate voluntarily and can choose not to take part.
	You can ask any questions that arise before deciding on participating.
	You are at least 18 years old.



If you have any questions, concerns or complaints, please contact: Dr. Stefan Feuerriegel (feuerriegel@lmu.de).



By selecting "I consent to participate", you consent to the terms and conditions described above.
